nodes.text: Barrarro was a male Wookiee, who lived on the planet Cularin during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.

Barrarro was the leader of Kiirloor, a Wookiee settlement that was located on Cularin, near to Cloud Mountain. During the time of the Clone Wars, the heroes of Cularin traveled to Kiirloor and Barrarro greeted them on their arrival there.
